I dont know where to place the code for them to teleport to X,Y. I need some help. If you would add me on skype, that would be best, but an answer on here can help. Its hard for me to explain.

item.title: Trying to Code Teleport Options [PI]
item.dc:creator: @PvPXile PvPXile
item.description:
@PvPXile wrote:

Well, click the option in game, in the client prompt it will outprint the case number e.g 646

You would then add case 646 in clickingbuttons.java or actionhandler.java, i’m not familiar with PI, then you would add a start teleport and a sendmessage if you want.
